22 March - Sfinge in fretta from Signora Scalfani

- 1 kilo semolina flour
- 2 liters water
- 2 tablespoon sugar
- 4 eggs

Boil the water with the sugar (Add liqueur of choice if you wish). Add flour to boiling water, turn off flame and stir the flour until it thickens. Spread on table to cool. Incorporate eggs to the cooled mixture. Put some oil on a board and shape into "e" or rounds. Fry in Spagnola oil. Drizzle with honey, or sugar, or sugar with cinnamon.  